    FilterGallery.Selected.TicketTypes="Tickets on hold",

        UpdateContext({datetype:Text(DateAdd(DateValue(Text(Today()), "en"), -3)),type:"Tickets older than 3 days"}),

        UpdateContext({datetype:Text(DateAdd(DateValue(Text(Today()), "en"), 0)),type:"Tickets closed today"}),

        UpdateContext({datetype:Text(DateAdd(DateValue(Text(Today()), "en"), 0)),type:"Tickets opened today"}))
